'''Lake Weir''' was a [[lake]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Melida/Daan/Legends|Melida/Daan]]. It was the only body of [[Water/Legends|water]] near [[Zehava]] for a large distance. Originally, a [[Hall of Evidence]] was located above the lake, floating on [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlifts]]; however, with [[the Young]]'s victory and the end of the war, it was destroyed by [[Nield]] and members of the Young forces as an initiative for peace.

Nield enjoyed spending time at Lake Weir as a child.

